  "ok": false,
  "error": {
    "code": "UNAVAILABLE",
    "message": "Error: Realtime transcription provider \"xai\" is not configured"
  }
}
```

After the completed fix, patched source Gateway on a separate local port with channels skipped:

```json
{
  "activeProvider": "xai",
  "providers": [
    {
      "id": "xai",
      "configured": true,
      "transports": ["gateway-relay"],
      "brains": ["none"]
    }
  ]
}
```

```json
